kradio (0.3.0-snapshot-2004-02-22e) unstable; urgency=low

  * fix several annoyances in configuration dialog, such as
    a reasonable minimum size of that dialog
  * recording buffer management is now configurable
  * preset file storage location is now configurable
  * finally fixed segfaults that occurred when calling
    virtual methods of virtual base classes in destructors
    (application exit and scan-dialog closing). Some
    compilers seem to not handle this case automatically in
    the correct manner.
  * add button for sleep countdown to display plugin

 -- Ernst Martin Witte <emw@users.sourceforge.net>  Mon, 22 Feb 2004 13:36:12 +0100

kradio (0.3.0-snapshot-2004-02-21) unstable; urgency=low

  * no more unnecessary redraws in recording monitor
  * improved behavior of quickbar: poweron/off
    automatically if necessary
  * only redraw necessary parts in recording monitor
  * split kapplication & pluginmanager
  * enable multiple "instances" 
  * cleanup IErrorLog usage
  * use threading for recording/encoding

 -- Ernst Martin Witte <emw@users.sourceforge.net>  Mon, 21 Feb 2004 18:07:43 +0100

